12:13 ti/ ga/r e)stin o(\ h(ssw/qhte u(pe\r ta\j loipa\j e)kklhsi/aj, ei) mh\ o(/ti au)to\j e)gw\ ou) katena/rkhsa u(mw=n; xari/sasqe/ moi th\n a)diki/an tau/thn.
