12:15 e)gw\ de\ h(/dista dapanh/sw kai\ e)kdapanhqh/somai u(pe\r tw=n yuxw=n u(mw=n. ei) perissote/rwj u(ma=j a)gapw=, h(=tton a)gapw=mai; 12:16 )/Estw de/, e)gw\ ou) kateba/rhsa u(ma=j: a)lla\ u(pa/rxwn panou=rgoj do/lw| u(ma=j e)/labon.
