13:7 eu)xo/meqa de\ pro\j to\n qeo\n mh\ poih=sai u(ma=j kako\n mhde/n, ou)x i(/na h(mei=j do/kimoi fanw=men, a)ll' i(/na u(mei=j to\ kalo\n poih=te, h(mei=j de\ w(j a)do/kimoi w)=men.
13:8 ou) ga\r duna/meqa/ ti kata\ th=j a)lhqei/aj, a)lla\ u(pe\r th=j a)lhqei/aj.
